  "detailed_description": "<strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 1980s arcade game action mixed with tactical elements and upgrades.<br></li><li> Vector-style graphics.<br></li><li> 26 unique levels to explore. <br></li><li> High-score tables.<br></li><li> Destroy your enemies and take their weapons.<br></li><li> Collect upgrade containers, boost your ship's shield, thrusters and armor, and upgrade your weapons.<br></li><li> 8 unique weapons + hyperspace/teleport to take you out of sticky situations.<br></li><li> Tactical elements: choose your routes carefully, pick the best weapon to use in each situation, try to pit the two enemy factions against each other.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 1980s arcade game action mixed with tactical elements and upgrades.<br></li><li> Vector-style graphics.<br></li><li> 26 unique levels to explore. <br></li><li> High-score tables.<br></li><li> Destroy your enemies and take their weapons.<br></li><li> Collect upgrade containers, boost your ship's shield, thrusters and armor, and upgrade your weapons.<br></li><li> 8 unique weapons + hyperspace/teleport to take you out of sticky situations.<br></li><li> Tactical elements: choose your routes carefully, pick the best weapon to use in each situation, try to pit the two enemy factions against each other.</li></ul>",
